  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37684</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ミラルドさんは
&lt;KLA&gt;さんの奥さんなんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is Miraldo your wife, &lt;KLA&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <StructId>1</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38064</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あいつは単なる助手だ、
そういうのとは違う</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She’s just an assistant, nothing like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <StructId>2</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38460</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……え？　でも恋人同士みたいな
話だったし……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Huh? But it sounded like you were a couple...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <StructId>3</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38928</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>違う。断じて違う</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No. Absolutely not.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <StructId>4</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……どうしてそんな
むきになるんですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Why are you so defensive about it?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <StructId>5</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40656</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;MEL&gt;、興味本位で
そういうこと聞かないの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;MEL&gt;, don’t ask things like that out of curiosity.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <StructId>6</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41304</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだ。君にはまだ
こういう話は早い</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That’s right. You’re still too young for this kind of talk.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <StructId>7</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41832</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>早くはないと、思いますけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But I don't think it's too early...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42000</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ……ってことはやっぱり、
おふたりは恋人同士なんですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah... So you two are really a couple, then.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうしてそうなるんだ。
違うと言ったら、違う</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How did it come to that? I said no, so it's no.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <StructId>10</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>18</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ、どういう関係ですか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Then, what is your relationship?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <StructId>11</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44068</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、&lt;MEL&gt;ってば……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah, &lt;MEL&gt;... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <StructId>12</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_019_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もう……女の子なんだかラ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Geez... Are you a girl or what?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <StructId>13</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
